## getKeys type

获取 对象 的 所有 key type

**Signature:**

```typescript
export type getKeys<T extends obj> = Equal<T, any[]> extends true ? never : keyof T;
```
**References:** [obj](./types.obj.md)<!-- -->, [Equal](./types.equal.md)

## Example


```ts
type f = getKeys<{ name: string; age: number }> // name | age
```
